      "id": "note--b5c6d7e8-9f0a-1b2c-3d4e-5f6a7b8c9d0e",
      "created": "2026-05-01T18:30:00Z",
      "modified": "2026-05-01T18:30:00Z",
      "content": "Investigation by GHOST / Breakglass Intelligence. Source: @smica83 tweet on 2026-05-01. Panel is active and operational. No victim data was found exposed without authentication. MaaS commercial model confirmed via CSS pricing components. Both IPs are Cloudflare shared CDN addresses and should NOT be used for IP-based blocking as they serve many legitimate domains.",
